ModifyableTopology, Object3DSpace, RelationTopology, Space, Torus
public class OrderedMulti3DTorus
extends OrderedMulti3DGrid
implements Torus

A torus that can hold more than one object in its cells. The cells themselves store their occupants in order of insertion, The list of objects in a cell contains the first object inserted at the beginning of the list and the last object inserted at the end. The object returned by getObject is a OrderedMulti2DLocation.
